'''Thene Campus''' was a campus at the [[Imperial University of Marngar III]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Marngar III]].

[[Benald Orlan]] attended Thene Campus before betraying his family to the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Empire]].

